Class Edge

java.lang.Object
Edge
public class Edge
extends java.lang.Object
An Edge represents a relationship between two vertices.

    • equals

      public boolean equals​(java.lang.Object obj)
      Return true if two edges are equal. Edges are equal if the source and destination are equal. Weight is not considered.
      Overrides:
      equals in class java.lang.Object
      Parameters:

    • hashCode

      public int hashCode()
